A normal young person can have a profile on numerous collective pages, from Facebook to Xanga, and can even link them to other services, such as Twitter or last.fm which offers a list of their musical habits, then these can be included in a tracking system like FriendFeed or Blip.fm, can also have a blog, in which the latest photo galleries that are automatically stored on Flickr or Picasa appear.
